<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AD Connect - Email Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      background-color: #f0f4ff;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">AD Connect</div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your email address:</p>
      <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
      <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Do not share it with anyone for security reasons.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="note">
      If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; AD Connect | All rights reserved
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>